 <div class="story"><p>Kitty Hawk Landing is a waterfront community in Kitty Hawk with a mixture of sound front and canal front properties. Water views abound with open water views of the Albemarle Sound available from not only the sound front lots but also for the canal front lots on the west side of Ivy Lane. The community of Kitty Hawk Landing boasts a picnic area with a boat ramp and a deeded semi-oceanfront parking lot for a private community beach access. There is an active Home Owners Association.</p><p>  <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/kitty hawk landing covenants.pdf" title="Kitty Hawk Landing Covenants 1">Kitty Hawk Landing Covenants 1</a> & <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/kitty hawk landing covenants 1.pdf" title="Kitty Hawk Landing Covenants 2"> 2</a> & <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/kitty-hawk-landing-covenants-amended.pdf" title="Kitty Hawk Landing Covenants Amended"> Kitty Hawk Landing Covenants Amended</a> & <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/kitty-hawk-landing-covenants-sec5.pdf" title="Kitty Hawk Landing Covenants Sec 5"> Kitty Hawk Landing Covenants Sec 5</a> & <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/kitty-hawk-landing-bylaws.pdf" title="Kitty Hawk Landing Bylaws"> Kitty Hawk Landing Bylaws</a>   - - - <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/Covenant-Disclaimer.asp" target="_blank"><b>    *</b></a></p>
